{"tid":1946164,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"【黃色經濟圈】【黃到金 Yellow Almost Golden】黃店外賣手機App（準備）上線啦！","createTime":"2020-03-27T12:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T16:33:19.000Z","uid":63750,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"23f5015e01ccb97a8dacd372cf8fa4f943943a6a","tid":1946164,"uid":63750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:25:02.000Z","msg":"小弟公司未有得WFH，但今日放AL，下晝肚餓想叫外賣，發現Food Panda同Deliveroo都仲有得叫Starbucks/老麥/吉野家呢D藍店（just to name a few），突然覺得，普羅大眾要食黃店，要全力幫襯黃色經濟圈，都仲係要經過一重障礙，要手動，或者有好多誘因會唔覺意幫襯左藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以就突然心諗，如果有個外賣App，可以由開發到推出，由落單到送到你門口，都係由手足包辦，入面既商戶／廣告全部都係黃店，全個App都係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">黃到金</span></span></strong>，全個App都係幫助緊<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">黃色經濟圈</span></span></strong>發大，雖然唔係咩創新既Idea，但我覺得係疫情期間，係經常有人帶風向話運動開始降溫期間，大家搞到一個有聲有色既黃店外賣App就正正係表達香港人決心既其中一個途徑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個App既願景就係第時會見到一街都係步兵著住黃到金既POLO衫，拎住黃到金既紙袋，送黃店既野食去你Office/屋企，大家都可以係生活層面上表態，<br />\n將來搞得好好睇睇既話，黃色經濟圈就唔會再只係一個熱潮，而係大家既日常生活，仲可以加速藍店收皮，<br />\n<br />\n正如之前搞全球登報個位巴打家樂牌通心粉講過：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">將革命融入生活中每一個層面，將生活變成革命。<br />\n你每一個消費選擇、工作表現、生活決定，<br />\n都可以係革命嘅一部分。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以開左個眾籌Page，如果籌到錢就即刻全力去開發，籌唔到就全部錢退番俾手足，<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JfJTLM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JfJTLM&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fkBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=58a2084f\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JfJTLM</a><br />\n如果各位手足覺得有得諗既，有相關知識想出一分力既歡迎入TG Channel，或者有咩意見提出，都歡迎求插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/yellowalmostgolden\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyellowalmostgolden&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fkBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=eebc186e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/yellowalmostgolden</a><br />\n<br />\n利申：打完篇文/Post之前都仲好懷疑有無可能，但唔打/唔Post就一定無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e14c1a97a6d4fb40c4c8c8b6ae778b2a8abb51","tid":1946164,"uid":63750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"新ＰＯＳＴ自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb5b793fe6ee23c56b73e65d4497372770f3703","tid":1946164,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:33:27.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"bd5c2a86a1b66cd9286f01a9842ce020f872b600","tid":1946164,"uid":63750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:36:25.000Z","msg":"再輕輕一推，多Ｄ人睇到支持下／屌下都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca61a6661fdfada75374ba7eb9b05d968373d02","tid":1946164,"uid":63750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:53:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"815a71b01d19afc885a9e4bd99d7a6d01f63bcf8","tid":1946164,"uid":63750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:27:15.000Z","msg":"Push呀"},{"pid":"445a85523cb8f97ad27758833de873f599adbbc4","tid":1946164,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T15:21:53.000Z","msg":"巴打試下去時事台開個新post啦<br />\n呢到d人多數用回帶/留名直接入post 所以好少人會留意到你"},{"pid":"42f38a2dc561d1a79204032c123e86cfc0db42b6","tid":1946164,"uid":117344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:32:08.000Z","msg":"不如一齊玩 #黃店外賣challenge #yellowshopchallenge?<br />\n<br />\n咁鍾意ig story tag人 不如整個#黃店外賣challengeaccepted?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1945867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1945867</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"31b5070a89aad6920510ff6ab983f6b33da61b18","tid":1946164,"uid":73161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:44:01.000Z","msg":"我見已經有人做緊，你不如加入啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm